<li sourcefile="commerce/tasks/base-price-trade-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Click <strong sourcefile="commerce/tasks/base-price-trade-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Save</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="commerce/tasks/base-price-trade-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Close the page.</li>
