<li sourcefile="commerce/tasks/base-price-trade-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="72">Click <strong sourcefile="commerce/tasks/base-price-trade-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="72">Sales price</strong>.</li>
